{"tid":2143971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Facebook員工可WFH至2021年7月；Google允許在家上班至2021年6月；Twitter建議永久遠距工作","createTime":"2020-08-07T11:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:05:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d502de12612b50587cee9db6c4c1c05491efd5c6","tid":2143971,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"Facebook發言人8月6日在電郵聲明中表示，「基於衛生和政府專家的建議及內部對於這些事項討論的結果，我們將允許員工繼續自願在家上班直到2021年7月。此外，我們將提供員工用於在家辦公需求的1000元美金補助」。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook表示，在政府指導許可下，將繼續有限制的重啟辦公室。然而，由於部分地區新冠肺炎確診案例多，許多美國和拉丁美洲的辦公室今年年底前將不會重啟。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle公司於7月底表示，將允許不需要在公司辦公的員工在家上班至2021年6月；Twitter公司也提出建議讓部分員工永久遠距工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/508163/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-facebook%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%AFwfh%E8%87%B32021%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%88-%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E8%A3%9C%E5%8A%A97800%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F508163%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-facebook%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%25AFwfh%25E8%2587%25B32021%25E5%25B9%25B47%25E6%259C%2588-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%258A%25A97800%25E5%2585%2583&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=1bcab15b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/508163/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-facebook%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%AFwfh%E8%87%B32021%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%88-%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E8%A3%9C%E5%8A%A97800%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"a9552133897e396bf19ae7bf7fc82d6e3093b616","tid":2143971,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"Office price <span class=\"xx-large\">Drop to $0</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/